Consultation within the community of Petit-Saguenay to establish a protection and management plan for the foreshore of the Anse Saint-Étienne. 
The study, carried out in 2007, includes: 


**1.** The protection and management plan;


**2.** The reports of the advisory committee;


**3.** The descriptive study of the environment (biological, physical and human components) and the analysis of potentials and constraints (ecological value and sources of disturbance);


**4.** A portrait of the ornithological potential.

notes_translated.fr:
Concertation au sein de la communauté de Petit-Saguenay visant à établir un plan de protection et de mise en valeur pour les battures de l'Anse Saint-Étienne. 
L'étude, réalisée en 2007, comprend: 


**1.** Le plan de protection et de mise en valeur;


**2.** Les comptes-rendus du comité de concertation;


**3.** L'étude descriptive du milieu (composants biologiques, physiques et humains) et l'analyse des potentiels et contraintes (valeur écologique et sources de perturbations);


**4.** Un portrait du potentiel ornithologique.

notes_translated.en:
Consultation within the community of Petit-Saguenay to establish a protection and management plan for the foreshore of the Anse Saint-Étienne. 
The study, carried out in 2007, includes: 


**1.** The protection and management plan;


**2.** The reports of the advisory committee;


**3.** The descriptive study of the environment (biological, physical and human components) and the analysis of potentials and constraints (ecological value and sources of disturbance);


**4.** A portrait of the ornithological potential.
